biography: Kristian is a golfer known for his meticulous approach to the game. A member of Master Golf Club, Kristian brings a level of dedication to the sport that few can match.

While Kristian has yet to capture the coveted Hector Trophée, he has participated in the event 3 times, displaying a steady commitment to the tournament and a relentless pursuit of excellence on the course.

Off the course, Kristian is known for his quiet demeanor and thoughtful analysis of the game. He is a student of golf, constantly seeking to refine his technique and improve his understanding of the sport. Though Kristian will not be participating in Hector Trophée 2025, his presence at future events is anticipated, as he continues to strive for victory and contribute to the spirit of competition.
